Package: targetsketch
Title: Create and Visualize Targets Pipelines
Description: A Shiny app for creating and visualizing
  targets pipelines (<https://github.com/wlandau/targets>).
  Simply supply a _targets.R file with the pipeline
  and supporting functions, and the app shows a dependency graph
  and manifest.
Version: 0.0.1
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/wlandau/targetsketch
BugReports: https://github.com/wlandau/targetsketch/issues
